title: Brand New Hardwood Floors, Wine Room, Newly Redesigned Kitchens
posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', "Conveniently located in Westminster, Colorado, halfway between Denver's central business district and Boulder County and ensconced against breathtaking and idyllic mountain scenery, Westcliff Apartments will not disappoint!", "Featuring one, two and three bedroom apartment homes with stainless steel appliances, upgraded kitchens and the largest square footage in the area, Westcliff is Westminster's premiere apartment community.", 'Call or visit us today!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Private Cabanas', 'Ceiling Fans in Bedrooms and Living Rooms', 'Gazebo with a Fire Pit & Gas Grill', 'Newly Redesigned Kitchens', 'Large Walk-in Closets', 'Built-in Bookcases', 'Wine Room', 'Linen Closets', 'Library & Reading Lounge', 'Full-size Washer and Dryer Included', 'Crown Molding Accented with Two-tone Paint', 'Fireplaces in 2nd and 3rd story homes', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
